column2: "As expected there's a lot more here than in the forest."
"Except the number of engagements are actually far fewer, almost like their aim is to run away. Or to look for something..."
"It's just as Regius said, something odd is definitely going on."
"Haha, sorry. It's kind of embarrassing that you caught me talking to myself. Please forget what I said."
"I don't know what you're after, but my advice is to not stick around here too long."
